EXAMPLE:
To save an entity:<br>&lt;cfset employee = createObject(&quot;Employee&quot;)&gt; 
&lt;cfset employee.setFirstName(&quot;Marcia&quot;)&gt; 
&lt;cfset employee.setlastName(&quot;Em&quot;)&gt; 
&lt;cfset EntitySave(employee)&gt;<br>To update an entity:<br>&lt;cfset employee = EntityLoad('employee', 100, true)&gt; 
